{"tid":1411451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持塞全日地鐵嘅巴打入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T03:45:13.000Z","uid":167971,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"71608bf2d34ee9ed94c3a01eb140340a9108e81c","tid":1411451,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"大家一齊罷工就係為咗表達訴求<br />\n其實基本上上晝阻塞咗交通就已經令到好多人唔洗返工<br />\n下晝開始就應該要俾人搭車去集會<br />\n最多塞到2－3點好喇<br />\n集會係一個非常重要嘅方法去利用群眾施壓同宣傳<br />\n而且唔好唔記得 集會通常一人多就會召集到好多人一齊做唔同嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以希望話支持塞全日地鐵嘅巴打要三思<br />\n咁做會唔會浪費咗各區可以召集一大班人嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97c26d0b9db39c7a8d975555d0805e620a10f7f","tid":1411451,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ceecb623be3d24e874aa4a8ab2ae71343ec40c6d","tid":1411451,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"各位巴打要三思呀"},{"pid":"8b40bcd5aa09f1054c78016a6d204f32b0ff0ebe","tid":1411451,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"塞咗地鐵就會少好多人集會呀"}]}